/* в”Ђв”Ђ REST TIMER в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ */
let restInterval=null;
function startRest(){
  let secs=parseInt(cfgRest.value)||60;
  restSetNumEl.textContent=currentSet;
  restTimeEl.textContent=secs;
  restOvEl.classList.add('show');
  speak(`Set ${currentSet} complete! Rest for ${secs} seconds.`);
  restInterval=setInterval(()=>{
    secs--;
    restTimeEl.textContent=secs;
    if(secs<=3&&secs>0) speak(String(secs));
    if(secs<=0) endRest();
  },1000);
}
function endRest(){
  clearInterval(restInterval);
  restOvEl.classList.remove('show');
  currentSet++;
  repCount=0; repState='idle'; phFrames=0; pendPhase=null;
  sesMin=Infinity; sesMax=-Infinity;
  repEl.textContent='0';
  setEl.textContent=currentSet;
  buildSetDots();
  speak('Begin your next set!');
}
