/* в”Ђв”Ђ MAIN POSE HANDLER в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ */
function onResults(results){
  const now=performance.now();
  fpsEl.textContent=Math.round(1000/(now-lastFT))+' fps';
  lastFT=now;

  cvs.width=vid.videoWidth||640;
  cvs.height=vid.videoHeight||480;
  ctx.clearRect(0,0,cvs.width,cvs.height);

  if(!results.poseLandmarks){ phaseValEl.textContent='NO POSE'; phFrames=0; pendPhase=null; return; }

  const lm=results.poseLandmarks;
  const W=cvs.width, H=cvs.height;
  const pts=lm.map(p=>({x:p.x*W,y:p.y*H,z:p.z,v:p.visibility}));
  const ex=EXERCISES[curEx];

  // Visibility gate for primary joint
  let primaryOK=true;
  if(ex.repConfig){
    const ag=ex.angleGroups.find(a=>a.id===ex.repConfig.joint);
    if(ag) for(const i of ag.pts) if(!pts[i]||pts[i].v<0.5){primaryOK=false;break;}
  }

  // Raw angles (visibility-gated)
  const raw={};
  for(const ag of ex.angleGroups){
    const [a,b,c]=ag.pts;
    if(!pts[a]||!pts[b]||!pts[c]) continue;
    if(pts[a].v<0.4||pts[b].v<0.4||pts[c].v<0.4) continue;
    raw[ag.id]=angleBetween(pts[a],pts[b],pts[c]);
  }

  // EMA smoothing
  for(const [id,v] of Object.entries(raw)){
    emaMap[id]=emaMap[id]===undefined?v:EMA_A*v+(1-EMA_A)*emaMap[id];
  }
  curAngles={...emaMap};

  // Form validation
  let passed=0; badJoints.clear();
  let activeCue='', activeJoint=null;
  for(const rule of ex.formRules){
    const a=curAngles[rule.id]; if(a===undefined) continue;
    if(a>=rule.min&&a<=rule.max){ passed++; }
    else{ badJoints.add(rule.id); if(!activeCue){activeCue=rule.cue;activeJoint=rule.id;} }
  }
  const total=ex.formRules.filter(r=>curAngles[r.id]!==undefined).length;
  formScore=total>0?Math.round(passed/total*100):100;

  // Score UI
  const sc=scoreColor(formScore);
  scoreValEl.textContent=formScore+'%'; scoreValEl.style.color=sc;
  scoreFillEl.style.width=formScore+'%'; scoreFillEl.style.background=sc;
  formEl.textContent=formScore+'%'; formEl.style.color=sc;

  // Coaching cue + voice
  const cueText=activeCue||(primaryOK?'Great form! Keep going!':'');
  if(cueText!==lastCue){
    lastCue=cueText;
    cueBox.textContent=cueText||'Move into position to startвЂ¦';
    cueBox.className=activeCue?'':'good';
    if(activeCue) speak(activeCue);
  }
  hlJoint=activeJoint;

  // PLANK hold timer
  if(ex.isPlank){
    const good=formScore>=70;
    if(good){ if(!plankStart)plankStart=Date.now(); plankSecs=Math.floor((Date.now()-plankStart)/1000); }
    else plankStart=null;
    const m=Math.floor(plankSecs/60),s=plankSecs%60;
    plankDisplay.textContent=m+':'+String(s).padStart(2,'0');
    phaseValEl.textContent=good?'HOLDING':'FIX FORM';
    angleValEl.textContent='вЂ”';
    if(good&&plankSecs>0&&plankSecs%10===0) speak(plankSecs+' seconds. Keep it up!');
  }

  // REP counting (4-phase gated state machine)
  else if(ex.repConfig&&primaryOK){
    const {joint,startZone,midZone,endZone,minROM}=ex.repConfig;
    const angle=curAngles[joint];
    if(angle!==undefined){
      if(angle<sesMin)sesMin=angle;
      if(angle>sesMax)sesMax=angle;
      const rom=sesMax-sesMin;
      const inZ=(a,z)=>a>=z.lo&&a<=z.hi;

      // Determine candidate next phase
      let candidate=null;
      if(repState==='idle'    &&inZ(angle,startZone)) candidate='atStart';
      else if(repState==='atStart'&&inZ(angle,midZone))   candidate='atMid';
      else if(repState==='atMid'  &&inZ(angle,endZone))   candidate='atEnd';

      // Frame confirmation gate
      if(candidate&&candidate===pendPhase) phFrames++;
      else{ pendPhase=candidate; phFrames=candidate?1:0; }

      if(phFrames>=CONF_FRAMES){
        if(pendPhase==='atStart'&&repState==='idle'){
          repState='atStart'; phFrames=0; pendPhase=null;
          sesMin=angle; sesMax=angle;
        }
        else if(pendPhase==='atMid'&&repState==='atStart'){
          repState='atMid'; phFrames=0; pendPhase=null;
        }
        else if(pendPhase==='atEnd'&&repState==='atMid'){
          const romOk=rom>=(minROM||MIN_ROM_DEF);
          const tOk=now>=coolUntil;
          const formOk=formScore>=50;

          if(romOk&&tOk&&formOk){
            repCount++;
            repEl.textContent=repCount;
            flashRep();
            coolUntil=now+COOLDOWN_MS;
            speak(String(repCount));

            // Set completion check
            const targetReps=parseInt(cfgReps.value)||10;
            const totalSets=parseInt(cfgSets.value)||3;
            if(repCount>=targetReps){
              if(currentSet<totalSets){
                setTimeout(startRest,600);
              } else {
                speak('Workout complete! Amazing work!');
                setTimeout(()=>{cueBox.textContent='нї† All sets complete! Excellent work!';cueBox.className='good';},700);
              }
            }
          } else if(!formOk){
            speak('Fix your form вЂ” that rep does not count');
          } else if(!romOk){
            speak('Use the full range of motion');
          }

          // Always cycle back to start position
          repState='atStart'; phFrames=0; pendPhase=null;
          sesMin=angle; sesMax=angle;
        }
      }

      const inCool=now<coolUntil;
      phaseValEl.textContent=inCool?'COOLDOWN':
        repState==='idle'?'GET READY':
        repState==='atStart'?'START POS':
        repState==='atMid'?'TOP / MID':repState.toUpperCase();
      angleValEl.textContent=Math.round(angle)+'В°';
    }
  } else if(!primaryOK){
    phaseValEl.textContent='MOVE CLOSER'; angleValEl.textContent='вЂ”';
  }

  // Heatmap update
  updateHeatmap();

  // Joint panel
  let html='';
  for(const ag of ex.angleGroups){
    const a=curAngles[ag.id]; if(a===undefined) continue;
    const bad=badJoints.has(ag.id);
    html+=`<div class="jitem ${bad?'bad':'ok'}">
      <span class="jname">${ag.label}</span>
      <span class="jangle">${Math.round(a)}В°</span>
      <span class="jbadge ${bad?'bad':'ok'}">${bad?'FIX':'OK'}</span>
    </div>`;
  }
  jointList.innerHTML=html||'<div class="jitem" style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:11px;justify-content:center">CalculatingвЂ¦</div>';

  // Draw skeleton
  drawSkeleton(pts,ex);
}

/* в”Ђв”Ђ DRAW SKELETON в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ */
function drawSkeleton(pts,ex){
  const badIdx=new Set(), hlIdx=new Set();
  for(const rule of ex.formRules){
    if(badJoints.has(rule.id)){
      const ag=ex.angleGroups.find(a=>a.id===rule.id);
      if(ag) ag.pts.forEach(i=>badIdx.add(i));
    }
  }
  if(hlJoint){
    const ag=ex.angleGroups.find(a=>a.id===hlJoint);
    if(ag) ag.pts.forEach(i=>hlIdx.add(i));
  }

  // Draw connections
  for(const [a,b] of SKEL){
    const pA=pts[a],pB=pts[b];
    if(!pA||!pB||pA.v<0.3||pB.v<0.3) continue;
    const hl=hlIdx.has(a)||hlIdx.has(b);
    const bad=!hl&&(badIdx.has(a)||badIdx.has(b));
    ctx.beginPath(); ctx.moveTo(pA.x,pA.y); ctx.lineTo(pB.x,pB.y);
    if(hl){       ctx.strokeStyle='rgba(255,51,85,.95)'; ctx.lineWidth=4; ctx.shadowColor='#ff3355'; ctx.shadowBlur=14;}
    else if(bad){ ctx.strokeStyle='rgba(255,51,85,.7)';  ctx.lineWidth=2.5; ctx.shadowColor='transparent'; ctx.shadowBlur=0;}
    else{         ctx.strokeStyle='rgba(0,255,136,.82)'; ctx.lineWidth=2;   ctx.shadowColor='rgba(0,255,136,.4)'; ctx.shadowBlur=7;}
    ctx.stroke();
  }
  ctx.shadowBlur=0;

  // Draw landmark dots
  for(let i=0;i<pts.length;i++){
    const p=pts[i]; if(!p||p.v<0.3) continue;
    const hl=hlIdx.has(i), bad=!hl&&badIdx.has(i);
    ctx.beginPath(); ctx.arc(p.x,p.y,hl?7:4.5,0,Math.PI*2);
    if(hl){      ctx.fillStyle='#ff3355'; ctx.shadowColor='#ff3355'; ctx.shadowBlur=16;}
    else if(bad){ctx.fillStyle='rgba(255,51,85,.85)'; ctx.shadowBlur=0;}
    else{        ctx.fillStyle='rgba(0,255,136,.88)'; ctx.shadowColor='rgba(0,255,136,.5)'; ctx.shadowBlur=9;}
    ctx.fill();
  }
  ctx.shadowBlur=0;

  // Angle labels at monitored joint vertices
  ctx.font='bold 11px "Share Tech Mono",monospace';
  ctx.textAlign='center'; ctx.textBaseline='middle';
  for(const ag of ex.angleGroups){
    const a=curAngles[ag.id]; if(a===undefined) continue;
    const pb=pts[ag.pts[1]]; if(!pb||pb.v<0.3) continue;
    const bad=badJoints.has(ag.id), hl=hlJoint===ag.id;
    const txt=Math.round(a)+'В°';
    const tw=ctx.measureText(txt).width+10;
    ctx.fillStyle='rgba(7,9,13,.82)';
    ctx.beginPath();
    if(ctx.roundRect) ctx.roundRect(pb.x-tw/2,pb.y-23,tw,15,3);
    else ctx.rect(pb.x-tw/2,pb.y-23,tw,15);
    ctx.fill();
    ctx.fillStyle=hl?'#ff3355':bad?'#ff8080':'#00ff88';
    ctx.fillText(txt,pb.x,pb.y-15);
  }
}

/* в”Ђв”Ђ MEDIAPIPE в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ */
let pose=null, mpCam=null;
function initPose(){
  pose=new Pose({locateFile:f=>`https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@mediapipe/pose/${f}`});
  pose.setOptions({modelComplexity:1,smoothLandmarks:true,enableSegmentation:false,smoothSegmentation:false,minDetectionConfidence:0.55,minTrackingConfidence:0.55});
  pose.onResults(onResults);
}
async function startCamera(){
  if(running) return;
  try{
    if(!pose) initPose();
    placeholder.style.display='none';
    vid.style.display='block'; cvs.style.display='block';
    mpCam=new Camera(vid,{onFrame:async()=>{await pose.send({image:vid});},width:1280,height:720});
    await mpCam.start();
    running=true;
    dotEl.classList.add('live');
    startBtn.style.display='none'; stopBtn.style.display='';
    phaseValEl.textContent='DETECTINGвЂ¦';
    const ex=EXERCISES[curEx];
    speak(ex.name+'. '+ex.desc.split('.')[0]+'.');
  } catch(e){
    console.error(e);
    cueBox.textContent='Camera access denied. Please allow permissions and reload.';
  }
}
function stopCamera(){
  if(!running) return;
  mpCam?.stop(); mpCam=null;
  running=false;
  dotEl.classList.remove('live');
  startBtn.style.display=''; stopBtn.style.display='none';
  placeholder.style.display='flex';
  vid.style.display='none'; cvs.style.display='none';
  ctx.clearRect(0,0,cvs.width,cvs.height);
  phaseValEl.textContent='READY';
  window.speechSynthesis?.cancel();
}

/* в”Ђв”Ђ EVENTS в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ */
startBtn.addEventListener('click',startCamera);
stopBtn.addEventListener('click',stopCamera);
resetBtn.addEventListener('click',doReset);
exSel.addEventListener('change',()=>applyEx(exSel.value));
cfgSets.addEventListener('change',buildSetDots);
voiceBtn.addEventListener('click',()=>{
  voiceEnabled=!voiceEnabled;
  voiceBtn.classList.toggle('on',voiceEnabled);
  voiceLbl.textContent=voiceEnabled?'Voice ON':'Voice OFF';
  if(!voiceEnabled) window.speechSynthesis?.cancel();
});

/* в”Ђв”Ђ INIT в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ */
applyEx('pushup');
</script>
